{"id":259121,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/10/维权网-上海维权人士集会要求18大关注民生（/","date":"2012-10-25T13:31:09Z","modified":"2012-10-25T13:31:09Z","title":"维权网 | 上海维权人士集会要求“18大”关注民生（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员孙小芸报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">24</span><span>日</span><span>上午</span><span>，上海维权者刘淑珍、鲁俊、何茂珍、顾国平、郭益贵、徐玮、王美莉、王秀芳、尤云、杨玉新、俞月芳、陈勤珍等</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>多人，在上海人民公园和平请愿：“迎十八大关注民生”</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-eo7kHq9Syr8/UIj_13FYvhI/AAAAAAAAR9c/70xLUsfmr_E/s1600/%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E7%BB%B4%E6%9D%83%E6%B0%91%E4%BC%97%E5%9C%A8%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E5%85%AC%E5%9B%AD%E2%80%9C%E8%BF%8E%E5%8D%81%E5%85%AB%E5%A4%A7%E5%85%B3%E6%B3%A8%E6%B0%91%E7%94%9F%E2%80%9DDSCI1329.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"221\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-eo7kHq9Syr8/UIj_13FYvhI/AAAAAAAAR9c/70xLUsfmr_E/s320/%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E7%BB%B4%E6%9D%83%E6%B0%91%E4%BC%97%E5%9C%A8%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E5%85%AC%E5%9B%AD%E2%80%9C%E8%BF%8E%E5%8D%81%E5%85%AB%E5%A4%A7%E5%85%B3%E6%B3%A8%E6%B0%91%E7%94%9F%E2%80%9DDSCI1329.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>参加请愿的维权者多数是为非法征地、强拆房屋、司法不公、医疗事故、劳动争议等诸多问题，上访时间</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>年至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>年不等。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>这些生活在社会底层的维权民众有个共同的愿望：希望十八大能够解决民生问题。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>维权者们多年不停地申诉、检举、控告，问题非但得不到解决，还遭受拘留、劳教、关黑监狱、打伤打残等迫害。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>大家表示要在十八大召开之前逃离上海，去北京等候十八大开幕，去向大会秘书处提交议案。要求释放被迫害关押的维权人士冯正虎、魏勤、毛恒凤、童国箐、王扣玛、朱金娣、崔福芳、邬玉萍等人。同时，也把各自的上访材料提交给大会秘书处，希望得到高层领导的重视，依法解决公民的合理诉求，将保障和改善民生作为政府工作的首要任务。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-4611217948907354097?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910]}